13 WHEREAS, increased advocacy, awareness, research and education may bring improved
14 outcomes for patients in earlier detection and treatment.
15 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
16 the members of this body express support for increased awareness of stomach cancer and
17 recognize that such awareness may lead to earlier detection for patients.
18 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
19 and directed to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the
20 public and the press.
